{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"13":"Divorce (Kitab Al-Talaq)"},"section_detail":{"13":{"hadithnumber_first":2175,"hadithnumber_last":2312,"arabicnumber_first":2175,"arabicnumber_last":2312}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2203,"arabicnumber":2203,"text":"Rapporté par Aishah (la mère des croyants) رضي الله عنها : Le Messager d’Allah ﷺ nous a donné le choix, et nous l’avons choisi. Cela n’a donc pas été considéré comme un divorce","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (5262) Sahih Muslim (1477)"}],"reference":{"book":13,"hadith":29}}]}